                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gavin",
                        "name": "gavin",
                        "displayName": "Gavin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Delayed due to lack of input and feedback.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gavin",
                        "name": "gavin",
                        "displayName": "Gavin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2006-07-07T21:42:35.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2006-07-07T21:42:35.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/10554",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gerrit",
                        "name": "gerrit",
                        "displayName": "Gerrit Thomson",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "A simple solution is to always use getConnection() to utilise the connection inside and outside the classes. Then give getConnection() a bit of smarts. ie:\nfunction getConnection(){\n        if (!$this->_connection) {\n            $this->_connect();\n        }\n       return $this->_connection;\n }\n\nNow getConnection() will always provide a connection or die trying ( actually throw an exception.)\nno more calls to _connect() in random places. They are splattered all over the db code.\nno tests for connection.eg   \npublic function listTables()\n    {\n        if (!$this->_connection) {\n            $this->_connect();\n        }\n....\n\n\ngetConnection can be over-ridden to provide a connection from some other place eg. Registry.\n\nCheers,\n   Gerrit.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gerrit",
                        "name": "gerrit",
                        "displayName": "Gerrit Thomson",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2006-07-17T18:08:29.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2006-07-17T18:08:29.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/11378",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bkarwin",
                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
